+/*
+ * The Ethernet MAC core returns an 8-byte Receive Frame Data Header
+ * with every frame consisting of
+ * 16bits of frame length, followed by
+ * 16bits of EMAC rx descriptor info, followed by 32bits of undefined.
+ */
